title: NSW woman charged over homemade gun - Yahoo7
text:
NSW woman charged over homemade gun - Yahoo7 A Sydney woman has been charged with possessing a home-made sub machine gun. Close VIDEO News break - February 20. Source: Seven News News break - February 20 
Amy Patricia Jenkins, 28, appeared via video link in Parramatta Local Court on Sunday charged with possession of an unauthorised weapon. 
The Kingswood mother of seven was granted bail to appear before Penrith Local Court on Monday, February 27.
